h indicates that these molecules can hardly be\nproducts of standard UV-photon and/or cosmic-ray induced chemistry in OH231,\nand that other processes (e.g. shocks) play a major role in their formation.\nFor NO, the model abundance is compatible with the observed average value. The\nnew detections presented in this work corroborate the particularly rich\nchemistry of OH231, which is likely profoundly influenced by shock-induced\nprocesses, as proposed in earlier works.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Dec 2014 17:16:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2015 10:36:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-01"}
