ers of\nmagnitude\\cite{Hohensee2013c}. We can also interpret our result as testing the\nrotational invariance of the Coloumb potential, improving limits on rotational\nanisotropies in the speed of light by a factor of\nfive\\cite{Herrmann2009,Eisele2009}. Our experiment demonstrates the potential\nof quantum information techniques in the search for physics beyond the Standard\nModel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Dec 2014 02:57:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Dec 2014 01:31:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-28"}
